    "synopsis": "In the aftermath of the Dropsite Massacre on Isstvan V, the Raven Guard are reduced from eighty thousand Astartes to barely three thousand survivors hunted through the caves and mountains by the traitor legions. Primarch Corax leads a multi-stage ambush against a column of Iron Warriors, looting the dead and waging hit-and-run war just to stay alive. On Deliverance, Praefector Marcus Valerius is haunted by a dream of dying ravens and risks everything to persuade Commander Branne to launch a relief mission against impossible odds.",
